org.jhove2.core.source
Class URLSource

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.core.source.AbstractSource
          org.jhove2.core.source.URLSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Source>, Reportable, MeasurableSource, NamedSource, Source
@Persistent
public class URLSource
extends AbstractSource
implements MeasurableSource, NamedSource

URL source unit. Represents source unit, possibly remote, that is designated by a URL using any of the following schemes: http, https, ftp, file, and jar. Redirection is not supported.

Author:
mstrong, slabrams
